name: icon-transfor
description:
A plugin to convert svg selected into background-image dataurl or base64 in your clipboard


  • only work in desktop now, will support browser later
  • multiple selections and convertions is supported
  • support dataurl and base64 data


Here is the git repository of the plugin: https://github.com/zhengpq/icon-export-for-figma.

If you have any question, please add an issue
